description: In "The Case of the Missing Milksop", Newcomer private detective Mason Jar goes off in search off the missing lactoholic, Sigmund Freud. But when the trail leads to the doorstep of Newcomer underworld leader Dexter Methorophan, Mason's in trouble up to his ears (or their Newcomer equivalent).
name: The Case of the Missing Milksop
To Live and Die in L.A.

description: With their manager held hostage by a face from their past, tensions among band members are on the rise. And the countdown to the concert of the year is on as The Clap come one deadly step closer to learning the identity of their rivals for a multimillion-dollar assassination payday!

volume.name: All I Ever Needed to Know I Learned From My Golf-Playing Cats
Amazon Woman and the Quest for Eternal Youth

name: The Ghost that Gave Away Gold

description: In the cataclysmic conclusion to the saga of Scarlett, the final battle between the forces of vampirekind and its hunters is fought in Houston...where the blood just keeps on flowing.
name: Blood of the City, Chapter 5

description: Rush gets an offer he can't refuse, or outrun! When a gangland massacre paints the streets red, Diego locks into a death race with the mob, the Feds and a mafia don who's most likely insane!
name: Running The Clock, Part 5

description: A mysterious case of a missing twin doubles the danger for Rush when millions of dollars go up for grabs! Diego is up to his wheel wells in double, and triple, crosses, and it's going to take every ounce of horsepower he has to reach the finish line in one piece! Meanwhile, in the shadows, a very powerful man continues his quest to destroy Rush!
name: Running The Clock, Part 4

description: Guest-starring Black Canary! Roaring down the street to your left: Rush, hellbent on finding the world's weirdest weapon of mass destruction. Screaming down the avenue to your right: Black Canary, with the same goal. Rocketing straight at you: Gearhead, half man, half car and all bad intentions! Who'll reach the WMD first?
name: Running The Clock, Part 3

description: In issue #2, what is Rush desperately racing through - and under - the streets of New York City to find...and why is special guest Black Canary also on the hunt? Jump on board for an adrenaline rush of sonic screams, hot motorcycles and fishnet stockings!
name: Running The Clock, Part 2

description: Master of action Chuck Dixon (NIGHTWING, Punisher) puts the pedal to the metal as a new hero burns rubber down the mean streets of New York City! When someone is lost in Manhattan - and time is running out - there's only one person to call: Rush! Who is the man behind the wheel? How do the scars of his past guide his future? And what is his secret to rocketing through the world's most exciting city? In this action-packed first issue, Rush is called in to rescue a young diabetic girl who must be found...before death finds her first!
name: Running The Clock, Part 1
